{"tid":465722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正聲明：悼念和平記念日既花叫虞美人花（common poppy),唔撚係罌粟","createTime":"2017-11-11T19:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T18:39:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7083ae3e29cb8db603bfff85ff7339f0699702ad","tid":465722,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:53:49.000Z","msg":"屌你cctvb戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯英國全國多地都有紀念活動，參加者都戴上紅色的罌粟花⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5a0700f5e603837e4c23c82f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5a0700f5e603837e4c23c82f&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhp4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1da2e1bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5a0700f5e603837e4c23c82f</a>"},{"pid":"5bbdbe0720da9002f27ffc161514c1925bc89700","tid":465722,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"In Flanders fields the poppies blow<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.flandersfieldsmusic.com/images/Poppies In Flanders.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.flandersfieldsmusic.com%2Fimages%2FPoppies%20In%20Flanders.jpg&h=d3f44041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2010/11/101111_life_poppy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Fsimp%2Fuk_life%2F2010%2F11%2F101111_life_poppy&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhp4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d9c82f33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fukchina%2Fsimp%2Fuk_life%2F2010%2F11%2F101111_life_poppy&h=8726b317\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2010/11/101111_life_poppy</a><br />\n...無論怎樣看，對於最後這一點有位紅罌粟的擁護給報紙發帖說，歐洲戰地的紅罌粟是Corn Poppy，即苞米罌粟，中文又叫虞美人（學名Papaver rhoeas ），而不是鴉片花的罌粟（ Papaver somniferum ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/64507/英國首相襟前的罌粟花/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F64507%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E8%A5%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%8C%E7%B2%9F%E8%8A%B1%2F&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhp4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=958106d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/64507/英國首相襟前的罌粟花/</a><br />\n...有趣的是，回到2010年，時值英國首相卡梅倫於和平紀念日前後率團訪問中國，於是英方成員無一不在襟前按例佩戴罌粟花。可是，此舉立即錯誤引發一場中英兩國之間的外交風波。當時中方成員認為，罌粟花會令人聯想到鴉片戰爭，挑起民族同仇敵愾的愁緒，所以要求對方把它除下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。惟英方拒絕，並稱「那朵小花」對他們有重大意義，因此所有人仍會繼續佩戴..."},{"pid":"882eee139ff0a3c54a122269d73bb5955024964e","tid":465722,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T01:20:28.000Z","msg":"洋紫荊都變紫荊花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人on99"},{"pid":"7bbb8c1367eed15d657f83fd2c15f04f548b25d7","tid":465722,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:21:07.000Z","msg":"尋日唔係正日就一堆人鳩叫<br />\n今日係正日反而無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31367dd67a390a0f0316821da10da3d23318a776","tid":465722,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b92